Description: Python Wires: Call wiring made simple
        =====================================
        
        .. image:: http://img.shields.io/pypi/v/wires.svg
           :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/wires
           :alt: PyPI
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/tmontes/python-wires.svg
